text: Kara-Bulak may refer to the following places in Kyrgyzstan: *Kara-Bulak, Batken, a village in Batken District, Batken Region *Kara-Bulak, Leilek, a village in Leilek District, Batken Region *Kara-Bulak, Chuy, a village in Kemin District, Chuy Region *Kara-Bulak, Nooken, a village in Nooken District, Jalal-Abad Region *Kara-Bulak, Suzak, a village in Suzak District, Jalal-Abad Region *Kara-Bulak, Alay, a village in Alay District, Osh Region *Kara-Bulak, Aravan, a village in Aravan District, Osh Region *Kara-Bulak, Kara-Kulja, a village in Kara-Kulja District, Osh Region
title: Kara-Bulak
